    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s reliable, stylish, and totally ready for your next road trip? I\u2019m parting with my car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really nice shape, runs super smoothly, and has been well-loved over the years. It\u2019s the perfect fit for someone who wants a solid, dependable vehicle that still looks great in the driveway. Come take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
