      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted driver\u2019s example featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant. It has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement. The chassis integrity is secured via subframe reinforcement plates, addressing the platform's known floor pan fatigue points. The drivetrain retains its factory limited-slip differential and a crisp 6-speed manual transmission. Recent suspension refreshments include updated bushings and dampers, ensuring the car maintains its signature communicative feedback and cornering poise. A technically sound specimen optimized for performance longevity.",
